This is the Readme for:
Simple

[Name]: Simple
[Contact Person]: support-compss@bsc.es
[Access Level]: public
[License Agreement]: Apache2
[Platform]: COMPSs

[Body]
 == Description ==
Simple is an application that takes one value and increases it by one unit. The purpose of this application is to show how tasks are managed by COMPSs.

== Execution instructions ==
Usage:
runcompss simple <initValue>

where:
		 * - initValue: Initial value for counter

== Execution Example ==
runcompss simple 1


== Build ==
buildapp simple
